Package ogdl

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IGraph
    A named graph node, with a list of subnodes.
    IPath
    Path tokenizer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Graph
    This is a data structure for holding directed graphs, where all nodes are Strings, except leafs that can be any Object.
    Ogdl
    This class contains some easy functions to parse OGDL (convert text or binary OGDL to a Graph object).
    OgdlBinaryEmitter  
    OgdlBinaryParser
    Parser for the OGDL binary format date: Nov 2005.
    OgdlEmitter
    Graph utilities
    OgdlEmitter2
    This emitter is for level 2 (cycles).
    OgdlParser
    Parser for the OGDL text format.
    Path
    Simple path parser.
